  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_131_000061",
    "sentence": "李皋，字子蘭，曹王明玄孫，嗣王戢之子。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_131_000062",
    "sentence": "少補左司御率府兵曹參軍。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_131_000063",
    "sentence": "天寶十一載嗣封授都水使者，三遷至秘書少監，皆同正。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_131_000064",
    "sentence": "多智數，善因事以自便。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_131_000065",
    "sentence": "奉太妃鄭氏以孝聞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_131_000066",
